{"type": "article", "id": 34251, "title": "在家办公？把餐桌翻上去就行了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-08T23:35:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 2604, "name": "Pearlfisher"}, {"id": 34729, "name": "Horus"}, {"id": 34730, "name": "Damien Regamey"}, {"id": 34731, "name": "株式会社博报堂"}, {"id": 34732, "name": "Reinhard AG Sachseln"}, {"id": 34733, "name": "有爱"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 137, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161109000059ipojXvK84DylN2cG.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>          </p><p>          </p><h3>Horus by Saverio Murgia &amp; Luca Nardelli</h3><p>虽然市面上已经有不少可穿戴智能设备，但鲜有考虑到视觉障碍人士需求的产品，研究机器人视觉的 Saverio Murgia 和 Luca Nardelli 为此设计了这款名为 Horus 的设备，希望能够帮助这一人群更好地理解周围的环境。它由头戴式耳麦和控制器组成，耳麦的一端配备了两个并排的高分辨率摄像头，能够将感知到的环境状态以及物体的位置、大小等信息通过触觉和语音系统反馈给用户。采用骨传导技术的耳麦可以让用户在听到指令的同时依然可以通过环境音了解周围的情况，比如在判定物体距离后会借鉴停车传感器的提示发出有针对性的提醒，方便用户及时避让。目前 Horus 正在意大利进行测试，预计将会在明年投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108232634YpOP3i2HRhUaknlE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108232634QKSmuR3UZfpFsad8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611082326330QtoJ5W3fgdpNcmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108232633swhQVOo4m5j0FTex.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108232633Yp0P12Udbn3qoImk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Pechat by monom </h3><p>不能陪伴小朋友的时候，让家里的玩偶陪他们聊天怎么样？日本<a href=\"http://www.hakuhodo.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">株式会社博报堂</a>旗下的创新工作室 <a href=\"http://mono-m.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">monom</a> 研发了一款名为 Pechat 的语音互动纽扣，内置麦克风和扩音器的它可以附在任何绒毛玩偶上，让分身无术的家长们通过配套应用远程与孩子沟通。除了提前录制的语音之外，这枚明黄色的纽扣既能播放歌曲，还有重复小朋友说话的“鹦鹉功能”，通过反复强化他们对语言的记忆。Pechat 正在日本的众筹平台 Makuake 上<a href=\"https://www.makuake.com/project/pechat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">进行集资</a>，最低价为 4740 日元，目前筹得的金额已达到目标的 2595%。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230133MSJrziUK0spoyuF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230133TfYCgnh0Uxl1zHRV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230133iA9cI3zW0GofDrNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230133JUrhiRKCzWcPqwbv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230133zwJREd7N0ltjif4g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230133YJzaGOr9U1BjE2XC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617886\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Whisk Wiper by Matthew Michel et al.</h3><p>如果你平时会做一些烘培，那么你一定对搅拌器上残留的面糊相当熟悉。为了让人们不再浪费这一部分食材，来自美国的 Mattew Michel 带领团队设计了一款名为 <a href=\"http://whiskwiper.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Whisk Wiper</a> 的厨具。你所要做的，只是搅拌前把这个由硅胶制成的工具从底部穿过，完成搅拌后就能用它把剩余的面糊给刮干净了。如果你有事需要离开，它还可以作为搅拌器支架提供支撑，让你不用担心面糊滴下来的问题。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2086970389/whisk-wiper-whisking-made-easy\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 23 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230448Sj2qPtpG9H1uKb8L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611082304483wlxovcZOUuSzHsn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230448GDzAueE7jb9ZpQB6.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"GIF\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230449PgM0W4NOw5seJzHY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"GIF\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230447G9Ns84uQnWHcvd3q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230448B9NylZrFLcm54DUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sence by Sence team</h3><p>随着越来越多的人开始重视自己的心理健康，对智能手环的需求也不再仅限于一些生理上的监测。来自美国的设计团队历时九个月的研发测试，带来了这款监测情绪的手环。Sence 和市面上同类手环的不同之处在于设计团队在对 22000 名病人的数据进行分析后制作的一套算法，它能够分辨出情绪之间的细微差异，根据团队的说法，准确度达到其他产品的 250 倍。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/455414429/sence-the-evolution-of-mindfulness-and-productivit\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 169 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230403HmdZSs1VnPQrxKAp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609940\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230404pw32jldB7IMa69Zs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635193\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230407DjhqTfNxtFS8E71b.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.486667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230408MrQRb62tC43Jjwve.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.486667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611082304036qU8Q9pT7iF5IErK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.855814\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230404MZcG4sFKxqhuIDYw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637155\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Celerina Table by Damien Regamey</h3><p>对不少人来说，在家办公需要解决的首要问题就是没有足够的工作空间，为此德国的 <a href=\"http://damienregamey.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Damien Regamey</a> 工作室为家具公司 <a href=\"http://reinhard-ag.ch/de/startseite\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reinhard AG Sachseln</a> 设计了一款名为 Celerina 的两用桌。可以掀起的桌板使它能在餐桌和办公桌之间切换，互不干扰。桌子内部的置物槽相当实用，桌板背面还可以当作黑板记录灵感或是贴上文件和装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230111f5Za1h9YjqmdyF2B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750795\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230111w6LrCiQqEBSbmp3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744703\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611082301100yEJ7pYMrawfScFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230110iIdp1bsNlULtDx7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fémme by Pearlfisher</h3><p>为了让更多的中国女性了解并且接受棉条，<a href=\"http://www.yoai.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">有爱</a>委托创意机构 <a href=\"http://pearlfisher.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pearlfisher</a> 为旗下的棉条进行了包括名称在内的品牌设计。为了最大程度地避免拿出产品时的尴尬，设计师们在隐蔽性和美观上都做了充分的考量：简洁的包装上只标明了基本信息并用包含了“女”字的 logo 做了点缀，强调了品牌名“非秘”所鼓励的不再为使用棉条而遮遮掩掩的理念。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230047zGWVmp1QtZlRAoh9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230046Bivd6C7m0q4wbpzW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.118000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230046tic0uQAxNW6qzPre.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230047W7p59euzwIRj0nCx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230047UhQpWAmqSMikeRt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108230046jKsfxwT813PUevq9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}